&num;rstats performance tip: if you must grow a vector in a loop, make sure there‚Äôs only one reference to it so that R doesn‚Äôt have to make a copy on each iteration.

&num; 6 seconds: x <- integer() for(i in 1:5e4) x <- c(x, i)
